casebody.data:
Alla OPENGEYM, petitioner,
v.
HEARTLAND EMPLOYMENT SERVICES, LLC. No. 18-5537. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 1, 2018.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until October 22, 2018, within which *309to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
